(4633, 386, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(4634, 386, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Separate the dough into two pieces and make a two large ball shapes. Knead each half with a rolling pin until they reach ½ inch thickness.'),
(4635, 386, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(4636, 386, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Now roll the dough beginning from the widest side and to finish, make 3 diagonal lines with a knife on top to allow the dough to breathe. Place the 2 baguettes on a greased baking sheet with flour. Cover with a cloth and let it rest for 20 minutes.'),
(4637, 386, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(4638, 386, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'After letting it sit, brush with egg whites and place it in a pre-heated oven at 392ºF. If you want to, place an oven-proof bowl with water inside the oven, so the cooking process stays damp. Cook baguettes for 20 more minutes and remove from oven.'),
(4639, 386, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(4640, 386, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'Finally, cut the tomato and the eggplant into slices. Fry the eggplant on the stove with olive oil and salt until soft. Now put the sandwich together and top with yogurt, chives and lemon juice. Enjoy!'),
(4641, 386, '_preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(4642, 386, 'preparaciones', '6'),
