(5936, 473, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(5937, 473, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Now add two tablespoons of the mixture in the pan and spread it, making a traditional pancake shape.'),
(5938, 473, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(5939, 473, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Cook for 2 minutes and flip it to brown both sides. Do the same thing with the remainder of the mixture.'),
(5940, 473, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(5941, 473, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'Now cook the corn, grate the carrot, fry the ham slices, and chop the lettuce and spinach into strips. You have to grill the zucchini sliced into strips.'),
(5942, 473, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(5943, 473, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'Spread a pancake with mayonnaise bottom and layer the vegetables, repeat it to make the cake.'),
(5944, 473, '_preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(5945, 473, 'preparaciones_6_preparacion', 'Finally cover the last pancake with avocado and decorate it with the sliced shrimp.'),
