(6773, 507, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'To make the marinade: In a bowl pour 1 tablespoon of olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, a pinch of salt, black pepper, honey and 2 tablespoons of soy sauce. Mix together until completely combined. Reserve about a quarter cup of the marinate.'),
