(7575, 559, 'preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'Sift the flour in a bowl and make an orifice in the center, like a ¨volcano¨ and add in the orifice the yeast and all the herbs, plus the butter and a tablespoon of salt. Now knead carefully and pour milk, mixing it gently until you get a soft and homogeneous dough.'),
