(7789, 571, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'Peel and slice the eggplants. Now place the slices in a bowl and sprinkle on top with sea salt until all the surface is covered. Let it rest for 1 hour or until they´re dry.'),
(7790, 571, '_preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(7791, 571, 'preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'Now wash the eggplants slices and squeeze them until they´re completely dry.'),
(7792, 571, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(7793, 571, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Then in a pot put a cup of apple vinegar, water and 5 bay leaves. Bring water to boil and only then add the eggplants. Let them cook for 5 minutes.'),
(7794, 571, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(7795, 571, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Now, you have to sterelize the glass bottles (you have to place them in boiling water in a big pot). Dry them gently and put in each one: red bell pepper cut into stripes, one or two bay leaves, a garlic clove, a handful of thyme, grated lemon zest or an entire lemon zest, one red dry chilli, and a pinch of black pepper. Now, cover all the ingredients with olive oil until reaches the top of the bottle.'),
(7796, 571, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(7797, 571, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'You have to keep the bottles in a dry-fresh place, without sun exposure. We recommend you to wait for at least 4 weeks before consuming, so the ingredients can blend together properly. The duration of the canned eggplants are 6 months.'),
