(8237, 599, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'On a smooth surface, sift the flour making a volcano. In the center, place the melt butter, the egg yolk and a pinch of salt.'),
(8238, 599, '_preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8239, 599, 'preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'Start by adding water little by little. Now knead the mixture until you geat a soft and homogeneous dough. If needed, add more wather to the mixture. The dough has to be soft, not dry.'),
(8240, 599, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8241, 599, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Once you have the dough, make some ball shapes with the hands and with a rollin pin stretch them until you get a rectangle larger than the sausage, so you can wrap it.'),
(8242, 599, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8243, 599, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Then, place the sausage in the middle of the rectangle, and sprinkle some grated cheddar cheese. Now wrap the dough around the sausage, sealing the corners like a letter.'),
(8244, 599, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8245, 599, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'Pre-heat the oven at  356ºF for 15 minutes.'),
(8246, 599, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8247, 599, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'Cover the oven dish with foil and spread butter on the surface. Now place the wrapped sausages and brush them on top with beaten egg.'),
(8248, 599, '_preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8249, 599, 'preparaciones_6_preparacion', 'Cook them at 356ºF until they´re brown, between 10 or 15 minutes. Serve them.'),
