(8303, 602, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'To put the dumplings together, add a tablespoon of the chicken and vegetables mixture on a cabbage leaf or on a wantan and wrap it. Now secure it with a thin rope.'),
(8304, 602, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8305, 602, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'Then in a bamboo steamer cook them for 15 minutes.'),
(8306, 602, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8307, 602, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'Meanwhile in a cup, add soy sauce and mix it with 1 tablespoons of toasted sesame seeds, 1 tablespoon of sesame oil and 1 tablespoon of chopped choriander.'),
(8308, 602, '_preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8309, 602, 'preparaciones_6_preparacion', 'When the dumplings are cooked, put them out of the bamboo steamer and serve them with the soy sauce that you made previously.'),
