(8397, 608, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'In a pre-heaten pan at medium heat, spread some olive oil drops and add the cubed onion. Cook for 5 minutes. Then add the chopped parsley and the shrimps. Now simmer for 5 more minutes. Add salt and black pepper, to taste.'),
(8398, 608, '_preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
