(8699, 625, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'Heat a pan at medium fire, and add some olive oil drops. Now pour the cherry tomatoes, the onion, the garlic clove, the baguette cut into cubes, and add a splash of olive oil. Stir. Now add a pinch of salt and black pepper, and simmer for 5 more minutes or until the baguette cubes are brown. Rerserve.'),
(8700, 625, '_preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8701, 625, 'preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'Then in a bowl grate the gruyere and the emmenthal cheese.'),
(8702, 625, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8703, 625, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Now in a small pot pour ½ cup of whitw wine and bring it to boil with the squeeze of a lemon and the grated cheese. Stir constantly and simmer until the cheese has melted.'),
(8704, 625, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8705, 625, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Meanwhile, mix the corn starch tablespoons with the cheddar cheese and pour into the melted cheese in the small pot. Now simmer for 3 more minutes until you get an homogeneous mixture. Add a pinch of black pepper and grated nutmeg. Rerserve it.'),
(8706, 625, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8707, 625, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'To serve, place the fondue in the table with the cheese cream. The fondue has to be boiling. Stir occasionally.'),
(8708, 625, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8709, 625, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'Finally, with a fork prick the baguette cubes and spread in the cheese.'),
