(8767, 628, 'preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'For the risotto cube ½ of a onion and fry it in a pan with a pinch of salt. Add the vegetables broth to avoid bruning, and the stir-fry doesn´t dry.'),
(8768, 628, '_preparaciones_0_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8769, 628, 'preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'When the onion is soft, add a cup of arborio rice. Stir and mix gently. Then add ½ cup of 120 sauvignon blanc. Simmer for 8 more minutes or until the wine has evaporated.'),
(8770, 628, '_preparaciones_1_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8771, 628, 'preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'Bring the cup with vegetables broth to boil and slowly the rice, until you cover all the water with it. Occasionally stir.'),
(8772, 628, '_preparaciones_2_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8773, 628, 'preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'Simmer for 15 minutes.'),
(8774, 628, '_preparaciones_3_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8775, 628, 'preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'When the risotto is ready, take it out of the fire and add 2 tablespoons of butter, a pinch of salt, parmesan cheese and pesto tablespoons. Check the flavour, and let it rest.'),
(8776, 628, '_preparaciones_4_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8777, 628, 'preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'For the tataki (japanese cooking method) sprinkle sesame seeds and salt on the tuna fillets, then pur them into a pre-heat pan at high heat with some olive oil drops. Seal it for both sides for 3 minutes.'),
(8778, 628, '_preparaciones_5_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8779, 628, 'preparaciones_6_preparacion', 'When the tuna is sealed, turn the fire off and let it rest for 5 minutes before cut it into sheets.'),
(8780, 628, '_preparaciones_6_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
(8781, 628, 'preparaciones_7_preparacion', 'For the bittersweet sauce, mix 2 tablespoons of balsamic vinegar, 3 tablespoons of soy soy, squeeze of a lemon, 1 tablespoon of tabasco chili sauce, 1 tablespoon of honey, 1 tablespoon of mustard, salt, and black pepper to taste.'),
(8782, 628, '_preparaciones_7_preparacion', 'field_58606bb7acb51'),
